        <h1>Privacy Policy for Tundra Painting</h1>
        <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> January 1, 2024</p>
        <p><strong>Tundra Painting</strong> ("we," "us," or "our") is committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring compliance with communication standards, including transparency in data collection and user rights.</p>

        <h2>1. What Information is Collected</h2>
        <p>We collect the following types of information to provide our services effectively:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, physical address, and payment information.</li>
            <li><strong>Communication Records:</strong> Opt-in records, timestamps, and history for SMS and email.</li>
            <li><strong>Inquiry Details:</strong> Service requests, appointment preferences, and feedback.</li>
            <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> IP address, browser type, and website usage patterns.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. How Your Data is Used</h2>
        <p>Your information is used to facilitate and improve our services, specifically for:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Service Delivery:</strong> Processing transactions and providing customer support.</li>
            <li><strong>Communication:</strong> Sending appointment notifications, reminders, and updates regarding your inquiries.</li>
            <li><strong>Operations:</strong> Enhancing website functionality and preventing fraud.</li>
            <li><strong>Compliance:</strong> Maintaining records of consent and communication preferences.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. SMS Messaging & Opt-In Details</h2>
        <p>By providing your phone number and opting into our messaging services, you agree to receive text messages related to appointment notifications, reminders, and general customer service.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Consent:</strong> Messages are only sent to users who have explicitly opted in; we maintain timestamped records of this consent.</li>
            <li><strong>Frequency:</strong> Message frequency varies based on your interactions and requested services.</li>
            <li><strong>Opt-Out:</strong> You can cancel SMS notifications at any time by replying "STOP." You will receive one final confirmation message.</li>
            <li><strong>Assistance:</strong> Reply "HELP" for support or contact us via email.</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="critical">
            CRITICAL SMS DATA PROTECTION: No mobile information will be shared with third parties or affiliates for marketing or promotional purposes. All other categories exclude text messaging originator opt-in data and consent; this information will not be shared with any third parties.
        </div>

        <h2>4. Cookie & Tracking Information</h2>
        <p>We use cookies and similar technologies to analyze site traffic, remember your preferences, and improve your user experience. You can control or disable cookies through your browser settings, though some website features may be limited as a result.</p>

        <h2>5. Data Security Practices</h2>
        <p>We implement strict physical, technical, and administrative security measures to safeguard your personal data.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Access Control:</strong> Access to your information is restricted to authorized personnel and subcontractors who need it to provide service.</li>
            <li><strong>Provider Standards:</strong> All third-party vendors (e.g., payment processors, SMS aggregators) are contractually obligated to maintain data confidentiality and security.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>6. User Rights (Update Info & Unsubscribe)</h2>
        <p>We respect your rights regarding your personal information:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Update/Access:</strong> You may contact us at any time to request access to your data or to update/correct your personal information.</li>
            <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> You may request that we delete your personal data, subject to legal record-keeping requirements.</li>
            <li><strong>Unsubscribe:</strong> In addition to SMS "STOP" commands, you may opt out of email communications by clicking the "unsubscribe" link in any email sent by us.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>7. Information Sharing & Disclosure</h2>
        <p>We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information. We only share data with:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> Subcontractors and vendors who assist in operations (e.g., scheduling, payment processing).</li>
            <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> When required by law, court order, or to protect our legal rights.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>For questions regarding this policy or to exercise your rights, please contact us directly at <strong>info@tundrapainting.com</strong>
